{"duration":"5ms","environment":"development","level":"debug","message":"Prisma Query","params":"[\"\n\nSomil Choudhary\n+91 8287156256|somil2005@gmail.com|linkedin.com/in/somil-choudhary|github.com/somil0701\nEducation\nGuru Gobind Singh Indraprastha UniversityDwarka, Delhi\nBachelor of Technology in Computer Science and EngineeringAug. 2023 – Present\nIndian Institute of Technology Madras (Online)Chennai, Tamil Nadu\nBachelor of Science in Data Science and ApplicationsMay. 2023 – Present\nExperience\nSoftware Developer InternJuly 2025 – Sep 2025\nAnsun Multitech India Ltd.New Delhi, India\n•\nRevamped and optimized a production-scale web application, significantly improving load performance and user\nresponsiveness\n•\nOptimized frontend assets andreduced page load time by\n ̃\n30%using lazy loading and code splitting\n•\nEnhanced UI/UX by redesigning key components for better accessibility and mobile compatibility\n•\nImproved performance across 10+ key pages, enhancing user experience for production traffic\n•\nCollaborated with the team to identify andfix performance bottlenecksand UI inconsistencies\nTechnical Lead (Volunteer)August 2025 - August 2026\nGoogle Developer Groups (GDG)Remote\n•\nSpearheaded development of the flagship hackathon website, delivering ahigh-performance, visually\nimmersive platformfor 500+ participants\n•\nMentored and coordinated a team, enforcingbest practices in frontend architecture, code quality, and\ndeployment workflows\n•\nDrove technical strategy by selecting tools, optimizing performance, and ensuringscalable and maintainable\ncodebase\nProjects\nFindMySpot|VueJS, ChartJS, Flask, Redis, Celery, SQLAlchemy, SQLite3, SMTPJan 2026\n•\nDevelopedFindMySpot, a full-stack parking management system withrole-based access control (RBAC),\nenabling real-time reservation, occupancy tracking, and automated billing workflows\n•\nBuilt scalable backend services handling 300+ concurrent users, with Redis caching reducing API latency by 20%\n•\nDesigned and deployed a responsive frontend usingVue.js, Bootstrap, and Chart.js, deliveringdata-driven\ndashboardsfor analytics (occupancy, revenue, trends) and improving user experience\nSIPE (Smart Interview Preparation Engine)|NextJS, Tailwind, ReCharts, NodeJS, Postgres, BullMay 2026\n•\nEngineered apersonalized coding practice systemleveraging performance analytics and adaptive\nrecommendations to improve interview preparation efficiency\n•\nImplementedtopic-wise analytics and weakness detection algorithms, enabling data-backed learning and\nprogress tracking\n•\nArchitected ascalable full-stack solutionwith optimized APIs, caching, and background jobs for real-time\ninsights and recommendations\n•\nDesigned for scalability with support for real-time user analytics and personalized recommendations\nTechnical Skills\nLanguages:  C++, JavaScript, Python\nFrontend:  React, Next.js, Vue.js, Tailwind\nBackend:  Node.js, Express, Flask\nDatabase:  PostgreSQL, MongoDB, SQLite, Redis\nTools:  Git, Docker, GCP, Linux\nExtra Curricular Activities\n•Solved 700+ DSA Questions on different coding platforms such asLeetCode, GeeksforGeeks,Codeforces, etc.\n•Achieved a peak rating of1278+(Pupil) onCodeforces,1440+onCodeChef,1557+onLeetCode\n•Strong problem-solving skills across data structures and algorithms, including graphs, DP, and greedy techniques\",{\"summary\":\"Somil Choudhary\\n+91 8287156256|somil2005@gmail.com|linkedin.com/in/somil-choudhary|github.com/somil0701\\nEducation\\nGuru Gobind Singh Indraprastha UniversityDwarka, Delhi\\nBachelor of Technology in Computer Science and EngineeringAug. 2023 – P\",\"experience\":[],\"education\":[],\"projects\":[],\"skills\":[\"JavaScript\",\"React\",\"Node.js\",\"PostgreSQL\",\"Redis\",\"Python\"]},[{\"skillName\":\"JavaScript\",\"confidenceScore\":0.75,\"yearsExperience\":1,\"context\":\"Detected by local keyword fallback parser\"},{\"skillName\":\"React\",\"confidenceScore\":0.75,\"yearsExperience\":1,\"context\":\"De